Memory Test

1.How To use ?

TestMemory.memory(this);

2.How it's work ?

It will Display the memory uses of the Device in MB.

*Getting the runtime reference from system
*Print used memory
*Print free memory
*Print total available memory
*Print Maximum available memory

Example 

Display in log while reading a message form DB

E/tag:  =================================
E/tag: heap native: allocated 9.49MB of 16.00MB (6.10MB free)
E/tag: memory: allocated: 13.00MB of 128.00MB (2.00MB free)
E/Heap: ##### Heap utilization statistics [MB] #####
E/Memory: Used Memory:10
E/Free: Free Memory:2
E/Total: Total Memory:13
E/Max: Max Memory:128


 

